The paper deals with the problem of combining multiple online learning algorithms with partial feedback, which is a core topic in machine learning. The use of bandit algorithms is also a common approach in this area. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which could place it in cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
